s. regulation in emerging CR environments.\nRelying on extensive GT simulations, some rules of behaviour - to be expanded\ninto techno-social norms - may be derived.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 13 Jul 2012 21:18:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-07-17"}
